data.description: A perfect home for a large family. Three bedrooms on the upper floor and two more downstairs. Upper master has a half bath. Coming into the front door, you can go up half a flight of stairs to the living room and dining area. From the dining room the large kitchen is to the right, A pantry is in the kitchen with additional storage just outside the kitchen. The three bedrooms and a guest bath are on a long hallway. Down stairs you'll find A large bedroom that can be another master or in-law suite. There is also another bedroom that can also be used as an office. The large family room is bordered by the third bath and a huge utility area. This home won't last long.
